&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Initial water = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(5\frac{3}{4}\)&lt;/span&gt; liters&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Water drained each time = 2.375 liters&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number of times drained = 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Remaining water = Initial water &amp;minus; Total drained water&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(5\frac{3}{4} = \frac{23}{4}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(2.375 = \frac{2375}{1000} = \frac{19}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Total drained = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{19}{8} \times 2 = \frac{19}{4}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Remaining water = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{23}{4} - \frac{19}{4}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Remaining water = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{4}{4}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Remaining water = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(1\)&lt;/span&gt; liter&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; The correct answer is &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(1\)&lt;/span&gt; liter.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><strong>दिया गया है:</strong></p>

<p>प्रारंभिक पानी = <span class="math-tex">\(5\frac{3}{4}\)</span> लीटर</p>

<p>हर बार निकाला गया पानी = 2.375 लीटर</p>

<p>कितनी बार निकाला गया = 2</p>

<p><strong>प्रयुक्त सूत्र:</strong></p>

<p>शेष पानी = प्रारंभिक पानी &minus; कुल निकाला गया पानी</p>

<p><strong>गणना:</strong></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(5\frac{3}{4} = \frac{23}{4}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(2.375 = \frac{2375}{1000} = \frac{19}{8}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; कुल निकाला गया = <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{19}{8} \times 2 = \frac{19}{4}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; शेष पानी = <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{23}{4} - \frac{19}{4}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; शेष पानी = <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{4}{4}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; शेष पानी = <span class="math-tex">\(1\)</span> लीटर</p>

<p><strong>&there4; सही उत्तर <span class="math-tex">\(1\)</span> लीटर है।</strong></p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expression = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\left[\left(\frac{2}{3}\right) + \left(\frac{4}{5} \div \frac{2}{7}\right)\right] \div \left[\left(\frac{3}{2}\right)-\left(\frac{5}{6} \times \frac{3}{4}\right)\right]\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(a \div b = a \times \frac{1}{b}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;LCM for addition and subtraction of fractions&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \left(\frac{4}{5} \times \frac{7}{2}\right)\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \left(\frac{5}{6} \times \frac{3}{4}\right)\right]\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \frac{28}{10}\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \frac{15}{24}\right]\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \frac{14}{5}\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \frac{5}{8}\right]\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\left[\frac{10}{15} + \frac{42}{15}\right] \div \left[\frac{12}{8} - \frac{5}{8}\right]\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{52}{15} \div \frac{7}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{52}{15} \times \frac{8}{7}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{416}{105}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; The correct answer is &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{416}{105}\)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><strong>दिया गया है:</strong></p>

<p>व्यंजक = <span class="math-tex">\(\left[\left(\frac{2}{3}\right) + \left(\frac{4}{5} \div \frac{2}{7}\right)\right] \div \left[\left(\frac{3}{2}\right)-\left(\frac{5}{6} \times \frac{3}{4}\right)\right]\)</span></p>

<p><strong>प्रयुक्त सूत्र:</strong></p>

<p><span class="math-tex">\(a \div b = a \times \frac{1}{b}\)</span></p>

<p>भिन्नों के जोड़ और घटाव के लिए लघुत्तम समापवर्त्य (LCM)</p>

<p><strong>गणना:</strong></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \left(\frac{4}{5} \times \frac{7}{2}\right)\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \left(\frac{5}{6} \times \frac{3}{4}\right)\right]\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \frac{28}{10}\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \frac{15}{24}\right]\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\left[\frac{2}{3} + \frac{14}{5}\right] \div \left[\frac{3}{2} - \frac{5}{8}\right]\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\left[\frac{10}{15} + \frac{42}{15}\right] \div \left[\frac{12}{8} - \frac{5}{8}\right]\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{52}{15} \div \frac{7}{8}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{52}{15} \times \frac{8}{7}\)</span></p>

<p>&rArr; <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{416}{105}\)</span></p>

<p><strong>&there4; सही उत्तर <span class="math-tex">\(\frac{416}{105}\)</span> है।</strong></p>

